1.	Inception Date in the Placements List when we are filtering by Placements
a.	As soon as you create the placement, this inception date will be the date of creation (it will also be this when the contracts have a period range);
b.	Once you have contracts, it will be the earliest inception date of the contracts as long as those contracts are not cancelled or NTU (not taken up) – please see rules attached;
